videos.description: Marques Bolden comes down with the rebound after Marvin Bagley III misses a 3-pointer and dunks the putback.
videos.headline: Bolden slams home offensive board

videos.description: Grayson Allen falls to the ground to come up with the steal and passes to Javin DeLaurier who throws down the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Allen steal leads to DeLaurier huge jam

videos.description: Jordan Chatman gets the pass in the corner for the quick release and bucket.  Boston College shot 11-16 from long distance in the first half.
videos.headline: BC is on fire from beyond the arc

videos.description: Gary Trent Jr. pokes away a pass in the paint and finds Grayson Allen up ahead for the dunk on the other end.
videos.headline: Allen finishes Duke steal with dunk

videos.description: Trevon Duval shows off his ballhandling skills going to the basket, but when he misses the layup, Javin DeLaurier is there for the putback.
videos.headline: Duke climbs back and ties it with tip-in

videos.description: Ky Bowman lobs it up for Jerome Robinson, who throws down a serious dunk against Duke to get the BC faithful on their feet.
videos.headline: Eagles soar for powerful alley-oop against Blue Devils

videos.description: Grayson Allen drives the lane and finishes with a pretty scoop layup while drawing the foul for the and-1.
videos.headline: Allen draws foul on layup for 3-point play

videos.description: Boston College's Jerome Robinson tosses up a three right in front of Marvin Bagley III.
videos.headline: Eagles' Robinson knocks down a three in front of Bagley

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. grabs the tough offensive rebound and then throws down the slam to get the Duke bench on its feet.
videos.headline: Carter Jr. with the offensive board and jam

videos.description: Ky Bowman drives the baseline and gets the pass from Steffon Mitchell for the two-handed throwdown.
videos.headline: Bowman continues his hot half with a driving slam

videos.description: Jerome Robinson fires from long range and hits a massive three in front of Grayson Allen to help BC pull the stunning upset
videos.headline: BC's Robinson makes huge 3 in upset over No. 1 Duke

videos.description: Boston College head coach Jim Christian is proud of his Eagles team for taking down No. 1 Duke and says his team can play with anybody in the country.
videos.headline: Coach Christian on BC win: 'They deserved to win this game'

videos.description: Boston College's Ky Bowman expresses his excitement for the rest of the season after a victory over top-ranked Duke.
videos.headline: Bowman: 'It's a big win for our team'

videos.description: Mike Couzens and Mark Plansky break down how the Eagles' 3-point shooting was lights out against the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: 3-point shooting key for BC in win over No. 1 Duke

videos.description: Ky Bowman scores 30 points and grabs 10 rebounds as Boston College defeats No. 1 Duke 89-84, handing the Blue Devils their first loss of the season.
videos.headline: No. 1 Duke falls to Boston College
